<title>Full Text</title>
<para id="fs-idm674031408">Excerpts from <emphasis effect="italics">Walker’s Appeal, in Four Articles; Together with a Preamble, to the Coloured Citizens of the World, but in Particular, and Very Expressly, to Those of the United States of America, Written in Boston, State of Massachusetts, September 28, 1829</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idm391619664"><link url="http://docsouth.unc.edu/nc/walker/walker.html">http://docsouth.unc.edu/nc/walker/walker.html</link></para>
